Package spring.model

Class Development

  • java.lang.Object
    • spring.model.Development
  • @Entity
public class Development
extends java.lang.Object
    Models a user's development. Maintains a uniqueness constraint ensuring duplicate entities with equivalent Idea and User mapping aren't persisted.
    Author:
    Shane Lockwood
